div.div: 更新人脸识别模块，添加Jittering特征提取方法；优化日志记录，调整识别阈值和状态显示；重构UI组件，提升用户体验

Ref/log (#11)
* 实施轮转策略、时间计算以及事务性轮转机制
- 新增了 RotationStrategies.cpp 文件，其中包含用于文件大小和持续时间格式化以及策略验证的实用函数。 - 引入了 TimeCalculator.cpp 用于精确的时间计算，包括时间间隔和对齐的处理。 - 开发了 TransactionalRotation.cpp 以实现具有原子性的文件操作管理，包括移动、重命名、删除和压缩操作。 - 实现了 RotationTransaction 和 TransactionalRotationManager 以管理多个操作并确保一致性。 - 为文件操作添加了错误处理和备份机制。 - 完全重构了UniConv模块和LightLogImpl模块
* 添加日志模块重构，新增核心、网络、数据库、UI、安全模块的日志记录功能，优化日志压缩和轮转配置
* Add face images and remove obsolete build scripts
- Added new face images: face1.jpg and face2.jpg. - Removed outdated build script: fix_compile.ps1. - Deleted deprecated project files: heschat_fixed.pro and heschat_fixed_v2.pro. - Removed quick_build.bat script for cleaning and rebuilding the project.
* 更新 .gitignore 文件以排除新的日志和二进制文件；在 FaceDetectWindow 中添加线程安全的帧数据处理和关键点缓存机制；重构 ContactCardWidget 的调试输出；在 MainWindow 中初始化人脸检测 UI。
* Add global configuration and safe Windows header; enhance face detection UI and management features
- Introduced `global_config.h` for UTF-8 execution character set and Windows-specific configurations. - Created `safe_windows.h` to manage Windows-specific macros and warnings. - Updated `win32tools.cpp` and `main.cpp` to include UTF-8 character set pragma. - Enhanced `FaceDetectWindow` with a new `FaceRecognitionWorker` class for asynchronous face recognition. - Implemented face management UI in `MainWindow` with options to register, view, and delete faces. - Improved error handling and logging for face registration and recognition processes. - Added functionality to save and load face databases, ensuring persistence across sessions. - Refactored face landmark saving to ensure safe file naming and character encoding. - Updated UI elements for better user experience and added help dialog with usage instructions.
* 移除 AsyncRotationManager.cpp 中的冗余代码，优化任务处理逻辑
